<h1>简</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#009900;">jiǎn</span><span class=alesi>(jian3)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 简 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 简</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/simple" style="color:black;">simple</a>, <a href="/dictionary/terse" style="color:black;">terse</a>, <a href="/dictionary/succinct" style="color:black;">succinct</a>, a letter</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 13<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 13 strokes: <a href="/character/想" title="xiang3: think, speculate, plan, consider">想</a>, <a href="/character/意" title="yi4: thought, idea, opinion; think">意</a>, <a href="/character/新" title="xin1: new, recent, fresh, modern">新</a>, <a href="/character/解" title="jie3: loosen, unfasten, untie; explain">解</a>, <a href="/character/数" title="shu4: number; several, count; fate">数</a>, <a href="/character/感" title="gan3: feel, perceive, emotion">感</a>, <a href="/character/像" title="xiang4: a picture, image, figure; to resemble">像</a>, <a href="/character/路" title="lu4: road, path, street; journey">路</a>, <a href="/character/满" title="man3: fill; full, satisfied">满</a>, <a href="/character/照" title="zhao4: shine, illumine, reflect">照</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/竹" title="Kangxi radical 118">竹</a>&nbsp;118.7</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 3 <br><small>Other HSK 3 characters: <a href="/character/卡" title="ka3: card, punch card; calorie">卡</a>, <a href="/character/担" title="dan1: carry, bear, undertake">担</a>, <a href="/character/静" title="jing4: quiet, still, motionless; gentle">静</a>, <a href="/character/句" title="ju4: sentence">句</a>, <a href="/character/检" title="jian3: check; examine">检</a>, <a href="/character/差" title="cha4: to differ; different, wrong; nearly, almost; an officer">差</a>, <a href="/character/层" title="ceng2: storey, layer, floor, stratum">层</a>, <a href="/character/树" title="shu4: tree; plant; set up, establish">树</a>, <a href="/character/角" title="jiao3: horn; angle, corner; point">角</a>, <a href="/character/皮" title="pi2: skin, hide, fur, feather; outer">皮</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-3" title="List of HSK 3 characters" style="white-space: nowrap;">more hsk 3 charaters &raquo;</a></small></p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 716</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 2954</p><p><b>Traditional variant:</b> <a href="/character/簡">簡</a></p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/二简" title="er4 jian3">二简</a>, <a href="/dictionary/书简" title="shu1 jian3">书简</a>, <a href="/dictionary/汉简" title="Han4 jian3">汉简</a>, <a href="/dictionary/白简" title="Bai2 jian3">白简</a>, <a href="/dictionary/短简" title="duan3 jian3">短简</a>, <a href="/dictionary/竹简" title="zhu2 jian3">竹简</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简介" title="jian3 jie4">简介</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简便" title="jian3 bian4">简便</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简册" title="jian3 ce4">简册</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简则" title="jian3 ze2">简则</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简化" title="jian3 hua4">简化</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简史" title="jian3 shi3">简史</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简单" title="jian3 dan1">简单</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简报" title="jian3 bao4">简报</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简写" title="jian3 xie3">简写</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简帖" title="jian3 tie3">简帖</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简慢" title="jian3 man4">简慢</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简括" title="jian3 kuo4">简括</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简明" title="jian3 ming2">简明</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简易" title="jian3 yi4">简易</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简本" title="jian3 ben3">简本</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简朴" title="jian3 pu3">简朴</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简历" title="jian3 li4">简历</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简洁" title="jian3 jie2">简洁</a>, <a href="/dictionary/简炼" title="jian3 lian4">简炼</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">簡|简[<span style="color:#009900;">jiǎn</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- simple<br>- uncomplicated<br>- letter<br>- to choose<br>- to select<br>- bamboo stri